            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1110.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse your<strong> canned lentils</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained lentils</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook, covered, for 2-3 min or until the spinach has wilted, the lentils are warmed through and the meat is cooked (no pink meat!)</p><p>Mix it all together – this is your <strong>fragrant</strong> <strong>lamb & spinach dhansak</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1110.-step-7-x200.jpg",
