    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fragrant</strong> <strong>lamb & spinach dhansak</strong> with the <strong>tomato & shallot salad </strong>and<strong> cooked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
